description: Demolition of existing community centre and part of existing warehouses, and erection of part four-, part five-, part six-, part ten-storey (29.42m) building containing 1150 sqm basement and ground-floor commercial space (use class B1/D1), with 69 residential units above (one studio, six one-bedroom flats, 38 two-bedroom flats, 16 three-bedroom flats and 8 four-bedroom flats) and 15 basement parking spaces, together with the erection of a single-storey replacement community centre set within new landscaped open space on Brooksbank Street. (Revised description)
